{"tid":1184783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有睇封神榜都知，推翻昏君係要搞好撚耐","createTime":"2019-06-04T00:45:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T02:19:31.000Z","uid":46849,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"03747ad5ff50859cbc23714b67baa6f45259eef7","tid":1184783,"uid":46849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T00:45:58.000Z","msg":"以前睇戲<br />\n會覺得d 人好蠢<br />\n明明民不聊生民怨沸騰<br />\n點解仲未革命<br />\n搞好耐死好多好人<br />\n之後先開始郁<br />\n<br />\n而家明白根本人類就係咁<br />\n所謂「早就應該點點點」<br />\n只係極小數人太心急"},{"pid":"cd33134d60c9d457befa70e8eae9f0b578795f55","tid":1184783,"uid":46849,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T00:50:08.000Z","msg":"好似美國咁<br />\n六四屠殺左 30 年而家先出聲<br />\n係我地角度好遲<br />\n係國際角度睇<br />\n其實只係一步棋<br />\n<br />\n所以有d 傻鳩以為行禮如儀<br />\n但其實係太心急<br />\n太自我中心<br />\n想一步登天"},{"pid":"eca028c12d682e58c045166f62c813af1b7061a8","tid":1184783,"uid":244332,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T00:50:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BSSpYPs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBSSpYPs.gif&h=88b0fdfb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b8814c610fd48e9f03a2ec83744f4a8676586b3","tid":1184783,"uid":46849,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"eca028c12d682e58c045166f62c813af1b7061a8","tid":1184783,"uid":244332,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T00:50:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BSSpYPs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBSSpYPs.gif&h=88b0fdfb&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T01:06:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲係好正氣既中國人"},{"pid":"0e2af4babe22bfa68b7aa1adb93b104984d3ea9e","tid":1184783,"uid":28195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"eca028c12d682e58c045166f62c813af1b7061a8","tid":1184783,"uid":244332,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-